        <subsubsection xml:id="subsubsec-evaluating-numbers-written-in-index-form">
            <title>Evaluating Numbers written in index form</title>
            <p>
               Index form means a number written with a base and an exponent (also called index or power). 
            </p>
            <p>
                <m>\textbf{How to Find the Value of a Number Written in Index Form}</m>
            </p>
            <p>
                <ol marker="1">
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Identify the Base and Exponent:
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Example: In <m>5^3</m>, the base is <m>5</m>, and the exponent is <m>3</m>.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Multiply the Base by Itself as many times as the exponent indicates:
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <m>5^3=5 \times5 \times 5</m>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <m>5 \times 5=25</m>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <m>25 \times 5 = 125</m>
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Record the final value: <m>5^3 = 125</m> 
                        </p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </p>
            <tabular top="medium">
                <row left="medium">
                    <cell bottom="medium" right="medium"> Index form </cell>
                    <cell bottom="medium" right="medium"> Expanded form </cell>
                    <cell bottom="medium" right="medium"> Calculation </cell>
                    <cell bottom="medium" right="medium"> Value </cell>
                </row>
                <row left="medium"> 
                    <cell bottom="medium" right="medium"><m>2^4</m></cell>
                    <cell bottom="medium" right="medium"><m>2 \times 2 \times 2 \times 2</m></cell>
